569
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:26,160
<i>... since the Reichstag fire.</i>

570
00:37:26,400 --> 00:37:27,520
<i>I don't buy it!</i>

571
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:32,080
<i>They knew. Someone knew
