572
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:34,480
<i>Brewer leads the cops into the theater...</i>

573
00:37:34,720 --> 00:37:36,600
<i>... and from the stage, points Oswald out.</i>

574
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:39,360
There he is.

575
