585
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:28,080
<i>No legal counsel was provided.</i>

586
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:30,320
<i>No record made of the questioning.</i>

587
00:38:30,560 --> 00:38:33,040
<i>When the sun rises the next morning...</i>

588
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:35,640
